I went to make it later

1187
00:50:02,360 --> 00:50:03,040
What do you think of it?

1188
00:50:03,800 --> 00:50:04,760
I think it is really nice

1189
00:50:05,200 --> 00:50:06,480
You can hold it, feel it in your hand

1190
00:50:08,480 --> 00:50:10,000
Does it really fit

1191
00:50:10,000 --> 00:50:10,920
ergonomics?

1192
00:50:10,920 --> 00:50:11,480
Yes

1193
00:50:12,760 --> 00:50:13,760
This

1194
00:50:13,760 --> 00:50:15,400
This is one point where I failed

1195
00:50:16,240 --> 00:50:18,240
I knew it

1196
00:50:18,640 --> 00:50:20,680
Then your croissant has arrived too

1197
00:50:21,320 --> 00:50:21,840
Where is it? Let me see

1198
00:50:21,840 --> 00:50:22,400
In my room

1199
00:50:23,440 --> 00:50:23,920
No

1200
00:50:24,480 --> 00:50:25,960
The croissant and that pen of yours

1201
00:50:25,960 --> 00:50:27,360
we took them back that day

1202
00:50:28,400 --> 00:50:29,880
Then you did not give them to me

1203
00:50:29,880 --> 00:50:30,840
You did not ask me for them either

1204
00:50:30,840 --> 00:50:32,040
You forgot them

1205
00:50:32,040 --> 00:50:33,120
Of course I remember

1206
00:50:33,120 --> 00:50:35,760
But you just kept them for yourself

1207
00:50:38,360 --> 00:50:40,000
Fine, okay, I will accept that

1208
00:50:40,000 --> 00:50:41,240
Take it back to your room

1209
00:50:41,640 --> 00:50:42,160
Wait a moment

1210
00:50:42,880 --> 00:50:44,560
You two are not done, are you, not done?

1211
00:50:44,560 --> 00:50:45,200
You keep playing

1212
00:50:45,200 --> 00:50:45,960
No

1213
00:50:45,960 --> 00:50:46,320
Wait a second

1214
00:50:46,320 --> 00:50:46,920
It is over

1215
00:50:48,320 --> 00:50:50,240
This gentleman, this lady

1216
00:50:50,240 --> 00:50:51,960
Let me play a piece for you

1217
00:50:51,960 --> 00:50:52,960
Come on

1218
00:51:00,960 --> 00:51:02,240
No, you two keep going

1219
00:51:02,240 --> 00:51:02,640
It is over

1220
00:51:02,640 --> 00:51:03,160
Do not all stare

1221
00:51:03,160 --> 00:51:03,960
It is over

1222
00:51:03,960 --> 00:51:04,240
No

1223
00:51:04,240 --> 00:51:05,640
My performance should be background music

1224
00:51:05,640 --> 00:51:07,120
It cannot become the main act, you know

1225
00:51:07,840 --> 00:51:09,040
He feels that after showing his skill

1226
00:51:09,040 --> 00:51:10,120
there should be some response

1227
00:51:10,560 --> 00:51:11,760
So, are you going to give me a score?

1228
00:51:11,760 --> 00:51:12,760
I have made it so obvious already

1229
00:51:12,760 --> 00:51:13,600
You still do not get it?

1230
00:51:13,600 --> 00:51:14,480
You want to rate it, right?

1231
00:51:14,480 --> 00:51:15,600
Do not score it

1232
00:51:15,600 --> 00:51:17,040
The score is too

1233
00:51:17,400 --> 00:51:18,440
too deliberate

1234
00:51:18,440 --> 00:51:19,680
Wait, I am afraid the glass will break

1235
00:51:20,600 --> 00:51:21,840
I will give you two thousand points

1236
00:51:22,160 --> 00:51:24,120
Yes, today deserves two thousand points

1237
00:51:24,120 --> 00:51:26,440
Refined into tears

1238
00:51:28,120 --> 00:51:31,480
is a kind of courage

1239
00:51:32,560 --> 00:51:33,800
You are singing me into such sadness

1240
00:51:33,800 --> 00:51:36,600
The fantasies from a few years ago

1241
00:51:36,600 --> 00:51:38,560
and the forgiveness a few years later

1242
00:51:38,560 --> 00:51:44,040
For one face you carry wounds all over

1243
00:51:44,040 --> 00:51:44,800
No, that is not right

1244
00:51:44,800 --> 00:51:45,880
Body wounds

1245
00:51:46,120 --> 00:51:47,160
The vase has been given

1246
00:51:47,800 --> 00:51:48,680
The feelings have been delivered too

1247
00:51:49,240 --> 00:51:50,480
Now seeing that she has understood

1248
00:51:52,760 --> 00:51:55,520
I am waiting for her to come to me

1249
00:52:03,640 --> 00:52:04,800
Can you make it flow a bit smoother?

1250
00:52:05,160 --> 00:52:06,560
Sung like this, my life feels so bumpy

1251
00:52:08,760 --> 00:52:09,880
I was wrong

1252
00:52:09,880 --> 00:52:11,200
I have wronged you

1253
00:52:14,080 --> 00:52:15,240
You are having so much fun

1254
00:52:15,240 --> 00:52:16,880
Play the ukulele a bit too

1255
00:52:16,880 --> 00:52:18,320
Can you teach me?

1256
00:52:18,320 --> 00:52:19,720
If you want to learn, sure

1257
00:52:26,720 --> 00:52:27,360
It sounds so good

1258
00:52:27,360 --> 00:52:28,280
Really, really good

1259
00:53:12,040 --> 00:53:13,840
How about you play and I sing

1260
00:54:00,360 --> 00:54:01,280
Lao Yu

1261
00:54:01,280 --> 00:54:02,320
So shy

1262
00:54:02,320 --> 00:54:03,600
Has he not always been this shy?

1263
00:54:03,600 --> 00:54:05,120
Then that day when we went camping

1264
00:54:05,120 --> 00:54:06,720
were you paying attention to Sunny?

1265
00:54:06,720 --> 00:54:09,120
I glanced at Sun Muyu's expression

1266
00:54:09,120 --> 00:54:10,640
like he was about to get beaten up

1267
00:54:10,800 --> 00:54:12,520
Do you think I am a smart person?

1268
00:54:12,520 --> 00:54:14,280
As long as you yourself are, right?

1269
00:54:15,080 --> 00:54:16,200
So you think I am dumb

1270
00:54:18,120 --> 00:54:21,280
Say bye bye to all your worries

1271
00:54:23,320 --> 00:54:24,800
One two three
